(3, '3', 'ki-s-3', 'Off-plan', 18, 5, 5, 'Dubai', '', 'Palm Jumeirah', '', 'Freehold', '', 'Duplex', '', '2', '8360.00', '', '', 'Furnished', '35000000', '', '', '0', '0', 'Published', NULL, NULL, 'English', '5BR Duplex in Palme Couture', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:12px\">Palme couture is a ten-storey residential building on the western flank of Palm Jumeira&rsquo;s trunk. It is being developed by Innovate Development LLC and houses a collection of fourteen &lsquo;couture&rsquo; residences. The residences comprise seven 3-bedroom lateral apartments, two 4-bedroom lateral apartments, two 4-bedroom townhouses with outdoor pools, two 5-bedroom duplexes with indoor/outdoor pools, and one royal penthouse with 4-bedrooms, a separate 3-bedroom guest house and rooftop pool. All suites are fully serviced with the amenities of a five-star hotel and arrive with open-air space, ample storage, two or three reserved car parking spaces and walk in closets.&nbsp;All homes have state-of-the-art kitchens with cabinets by Poliform-Varenna and white stone flooring. Amenities for residents include private beach access, black-tiled, saltwater infinity pool, beach club and juice bar. In the words of Massimo Lisotti, the senior architectural designer, &ldquo;The Los Angeles-style residences of Palme Couture stand as an archetype of experience-enriching design.&nbsp;The aim was to keep the concept free from visual noise, creating spaces where residents can connect and switch off. Each home holds a consistency of character: open space, clean lines and maximised glazing to highlight the view. In some rooms, it actually feels like you are suspended above the turquoise mass beneath. &ldquo;Clean lines, white open spaces, simplicity, indoor/outdoor as a unique all-in-one space, unornamented facades and seamless surfaces of luxury marble used as artworks and masterpieces of design.&nbsp;We&rsquo;ve imported fifteen types of marble from the Carrara marble quarries in Italy. One of the most striking features of the scheme is the dark grey &lsquo;Bardiglio Nuvolato&rsquo; marble fireplaces, a detail that sits in stark contrast to the bright white Volakas marble canvas extending from the corridors to the outside terraces.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n', 'JustProperty,JustRentals,Dubizzle,Propertyfinder,Bayut,GNproperty,Zoopla,Rightmove,YzerProperty,Own Website,Juwai,Mansion Global,PropSpace MLS,WallStreet Journal', '', NULL, '0', '0', '0', '', '', '', '0', '', NULL, '', '', '', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'No', 'ki-s-3', '2', 0),
